TextEng: "Draw attention? From who? What are you talking about?"
Text: "관심을 끈다고? 누구한테? 무슨 말을 하는 거야?"

TextEng: "An offer? What kind of offer?"
"Sorry, I'm not interested."
"What's in this for me?"
"I won't be a party to this horrible crime!"
"What do I have to do?"
"20,000 gold? That's not enough."
"Okay, I'll do it."
"Why should I believe someone trying to kill her own mother?"
Text: "자기 친엄마를 죽이려는 사람을 왜 믿어야 해?"

TextEng: "You're pretty open about this. Aren't you afraid of being found out?"
Text: "이렇게 대놓고 말하는구나. 들키는 거 안 무서워?"

TextEng: "You want me to kill your own mother?"
"I'll be going now."
"I want to ask you some questions."
"I have questions about this... mission."
"I want to ask you about something else."
"What am I supposed to do again?"
"I think we need to renegotiate our terms."
Text: "조건을 다시 협상할 필요가 있을 것 같은데."

TextEng: "What if I tell your mother what you're planning?"
Text: "네 엄마한테 네 계획을 말하면 어떻게 하려고?"

TextEng: "Why did Myrune banish you instead of killing you?"
"Why I should help you with this?"
